==English==

===Noun===
'''tilde'''  (''plural:'' [[tildes]])
# A marking used to show accentuation of characters in Spanish words.
# A key found on some types of keyboards.
# A character resembling a curved hyphen (~). ASCII character 126. May represent approximation.

